The President also announced the appointment of Nomfundo Tshazibana and Dr Rashad Cassim as Deputy Governors of the Central Bank for a five-year term each. Kganyago's second term will start on 9 November while Tshazibana and Dr Cassim will assume duty on the first of August. The Reserve Bank has welcomed the appointments.
